OL,5,G0005 24 Hours in A&E
OL,6,     FAndrew, who's 26, has been knocked
OL,7,     Foff his motorbike. Sam, who's 20,
OL,8,     Fhas been kicked and punched in the
OL,9,     Fhead outside a nightclub. And
OL,10,     FHenry's been hiccuping for three
OL,11,     Fdays.
OL,12,G0110 24 Hours in A&E
OL,13,     FThis episode looks at how life can
OL,14,     Fchange in the blink of an eye. A
OL,15,     Fwoman fights for her life after a
OL,16,     Fshocking random act of violence.
OL,17,     FAnd Tom, who's 12, has been hit by
OL,18,     Fa car.
